...last summer in July.

1539
01:55:02,380 --> 01:55:03,820
MAN:
Dominic!

1540
01:55:05,220 --> 01:55:07,300
Dominic, it's true.

1541
01:55:07,300 --> 01:55:10,380
You've come back.

1542
01:55:10,380 --> 01:55:12,380
Welcome.

1543
01:55:12,380 --> 01:55:14,220
[MAN SINGING IN FOREIGN
LANGUAGE OVER RADIO]

1544
01:55:22,100 --> 01:55:23,620
You look good.

1545
01:55:23,620 --> 01:55:26,700
Welcome, old friend.

1546
01:55:26,700 --> 01:55:30,620
It's like that story of, uh,
the Chinese philosopher,

1547
01:55:30,620 --> 01:55:32,820
you know, the one
I've told you about many times.

1548
01:55:32,820 --> 01:55:34,340
Which Chinese philosopher?

1549
01:55:34,340 --> 01:55:37,780
The name escapes me now.

1550
01:55:37,780 --> 01:55:39,420
The one with the butterfly.

1551
01:55:42,900 --> 01:55:44,740
Well, it's too long to repeat.

1552
01:55:44,740 --> 01:55:47,380
I'll call for a sleigh
to take you home.

1553
01:55:47,380 --> 01:55:48,900
I don't need a sleigh.

1554
01:55:50,780 --> 01:55:52,260
I'm going on foot.

1555
01:55:55,740 --> 01:55:59,300
The next time
the problem arises,

1556
01:55:59,300 --> 01:56:00,300
I shall know how to answer.

1557
01:56:03,060 --> 01:56:05,260
What problem, dear Dominic?

1558
01:56:10,900 --> 01:56:13,860
The problem which worries
all of us.

1559
01:56:17,980 --> 01:56:19,900
[GASPS]
Dominic?

1560
01:56:19,900 --> 01:56:21,660
Is it your teeth?

1561
01:56:21,660 --> 01:56:23,540
Is it your teeth? Dominic?

1562
01:56:40,060 --> 01:56:42,180
Should I lock up
the door?

1563
01:56:42,180 --> 01:56:44,540
The guest in Room 19
hasn't come back yet.

1564
01:56:44,540 --> 01:56:46,140
He went to the Café Select.

1565
01:56:46,140 --> 01:56:47,340
I'll call.

1566
01:56:50,300 --> 01:56:52,620
Yes, he came here.

1567
01:56:52,620 --> 01:56:54,540
He went into the backroom.

1568
01:56:54,540 --> 01:56:56,180
Uh, no one was there,

1569
01:56:56,180 --> 01:56:57,860
so he stayed only
a few minutes

1570
01:56:57,860 --> 01:57:00,140
and left without
saying good night.

1571
01:57:00,140 --> 01:57:02,660
He was, uh, holding
his hand to his mouth.

